RelatedSentence: BEIRUT - The general in charge of Syria 's air defense has been killed in fighting near Damascus , an opposition monitoring group and Syrian security officials said yesterday .

The officer , Lt. Gen. Hussein Ishaq , one of the highest - ranking officers to die during the country 's three - year conflict , commanded 60,000 troops in Syria 's air - defense forces , said Hisham Jaber , a retired Lebanese army brigadier general who closely follows the military in neighboring Syria .
